
**Privacy Policy**  

The TATTOO PRT app respects and protects the privacy rights of all users. To provide you with more accurate and personalized services, the EZTattooPrinter app uses and discloses your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. However, the app will handle this information with the utmost diligence and care. Unless otherwise specified in this Privacy Policy, the app will not disclose or provide your information to third parties without your prior consent. This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically.  

By agreeing to the TATTOO PRT app's Terms of Service, you are deemed to have accepted all provisions of this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is an integral part of the app's Terms of Service.  

1. Scope of Application  
a) This app does not require login and does not collect or store user information.  
b) When using the app's services, the app will only access photos from your device's album after obtaining your explicit permission. This allows you to upload images to the app's local storage for browsing and printing purposes. The app will not upload these images to any server.  

2. Use of Information  
a) When using the app's printing feature, the app records each printed image and stores it locally for easier reference. These images are not uploaded to any server, and you may delete them at any time.  

3. Disclosure of Information  
a) This app will not disclose your information to untrusted third parties.  
b) Disclosure may occur if required by law or by administrative or judicial authorities.  
c) If you violate any applicable laws, regulations, or rules, your information may be disclosed to relevant third parties.  

4. Information Security  
a) When using the app's services, please take care to protect your personal information, including uploaded photos and print records.  

